# Backend Rules — DEPRECATED (NestJS removed 2026-05-19)

This rule file is kept as a tombstone. The NestJS API server (`apps/server/`) was deleted on 2026-05-19.

Kupay now uses **Supabase only**:
- Mobile/web call Supabase directly via `@supabase/supabase-js` with the anon key + user JWT.
- Authorization is enforced by Postgres Row Level Security in `cost-share-app/supabase/schema.sql`.
- Mobile feature logic lives in `apps/mobile/services/*.service.ts`.
- Pure math (balances, splits) lives in `packages/shared/src/calculations/`.

See the current truth docs:
- `docs/SSOT/CODE QUALITY.md` (architecture)
- `cost-share-app/.cursor/rules/architecture.mdc` (patterns)
- `cost-share-app/supabase/schema.sql` (DB + RLS)
